                            <comment id="16570524" author="davsclaus" created="Mon, 6 Aug 2018 17:30:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Okay so this is expected to happen, because the validation is at the output, which happens after the message has completed being routed. So any error handler with onException does not apply here. (chicken and egg).&lt;/p&gt;
