                            <comment id="16570528" author="davsclaus" created="Mon, 6 Aug 2018 17:34:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;However there was a little bug in the validator somewhere else which I have fixed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16570574" author="davsclaus" created="Mon, 6 Aug 2018 18:09:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the unit test its been added to the source code and also a input validation variation.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
